cli.help.page.add_extension:
Pack extensiones ukar yatiyawinaka yapxataña (provider extension thakhiw legacy/schema-core)

Usage: greentic-pack add-extension [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  provider    Provider extension mantaña yapxataña jan ukax machaqaru uñstayaña
  capability  Capability offer mantaña yapxataña jan ukax machaqaru uñstayaña

Options:
  --locale <LOCALE>  CLI yatiyawinakataki apnaqata locale
cli.help.page.add_extension_capability:
Capability offer mantaña yapxataña jan ukax machaqaru uñstayaña

Usage: greentic-pack add-extension capability [OPTIONS] --pack-dir <DIR> --offer-id <ID> --cap-id <CAP_ID> --component-ref <COMPONENT> --op <OP>

`greentic-pack add-extension capability --help` apnaqam taqpach argumentos yatiñataki.
